<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
		<title>Andmeid</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/andmeid/css/home.css">
	</head>
	<body>
		<%- include("partials/header") %>
		<% if (user.id != 7276846) { %>
			<div class="notification">Currently WIP! This does NOT properly work!</div>
		<% } %>
		<div id="main">
			<div id="sheet">
				<script type="text/javascript" src="/andmeid/js/sheet.js"></script>

				<div id="sheet_fields">
					<div class="sheet_field" id="matches">
						<div class="explanation">
							<img src="/andmeid/images/example_matches.jpg" alt="Image of a ref sheet">
							<div class="text">
								<p>First, copy from one of the tournament's sheets (like a referee sheet) all of the IDs/MP links of the round's matches</p>
								<p>Then, you just need to paste that in the field below!</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<textarea class="paste" placeholder="Paste here!" onpaste="setTimeout(() => sheetIDs('matches', this), 100)"></textarea>
					</div>

					<div class="sheet_field" id="beatmaps">
						<div class="explanation">
							temp
						</div>
						<textarea class="paste" placeholder="Paste here!" onpaste="setTimeout(() => sheetIDs('beatmaps', this), 100)"></textarea>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div id="lists">
					<div class="list" id="matches_list">
						<h2>Matches</h2>
					</div>
					<div class="list" id="beatmaps_list">
						<h2>Beatmaps</h2>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
